data.description: Discover the perfect opportunity to own a sophisticated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom modular home boasting an impressive 2,076 square feet of meticulously designed living space, nestled on a sprawling 1.55-acre lot located at 1553 Cowpen Landing Road in Wilmington, North Carolina. Embrace the tranquility of country living while enjoying the convenience of being a mere 15-minute drive from the vibrant heart of Wilmington. This harmonious blend of rural charm and urban accessibility offers the ideal lifestyle for those seeking the best of both worlds.Gleaming hardwood floors lend an air of elegance inside the home, while the thoughtfully designed wrap-around porch offers a seamless blend of indoor-outdoor living, ideal for relaxation and entertainment alike. Discover practicality and convenience at every turn. Adjacent to the well-appointed kitchen, a generously sized laundry room beckons with its utility sink and pantry, offering a functional and organized space that streamlines daily activities. The oversized primary bathroom is a testament to luxury, featuring a sumptuous soaking tub, a walk-in shower for unparalleled comfort, a linen pantry for organization, and an inviting electric fireplace for added warmth and ambiance.Moreover, this remarkable home features a solar-powered chicken coop with automatic chicken entry doors and a spacious chicken run. Indulge in sustainable living, fostering a relationship with nature right from your property. The home also features two sheds. One of which has a rented water filtration system.
